00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:56,500
Anda mungkin membodohi orang lain dengan itu,
tapi aku tahu siapa kamu sebenarnya.

223
00:12:58,633 --> 00:13:00,467
Panggil saja tukang perahu, ya?

224
00:13:00,467 --> 00:13:02,133
Ini tidak akan berhasil.

225
00:13:03,100 --> 00:13:05,000
- Kita belum selesai!
- Mengapa?

226
00:13:05,267 --> 00:13:07,600
Karena kamu belum mendengarnya
apa yang ingin kamu dengar?

227
00:13:08,400 --> 00:13:10,233
Bahwa aku hanya berpura-pura
sekarang?

228
00:13:10,233 --> 00:13:11,333
Ya!

229
00:13:12,367 --> 00:13:14,033
Karena jika memang begitu
lalu berpura-pura,

230
00:13:14,033 --> 00:13:16,267
kamu juga mengakuinya
apa yang kami miliki tidak nyata!

231
00:13:16,567 --> 00:13:18,900
Semua yang kami lalui...

232
00:13:22,067 --> 00:13:23,267
Kamu tidak bisa begitu saja meyakinkan dirimu sendiri

233
00:13:23,267 --> 00:13:26,500
untuk bangun suatu hari dan memutuskan
bahwa hal itu tidak pernah terjadi.

234
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:30,067
Saya tidak pernah mengatakan itu tidak terjadi.

235
00:13:33,167 --> 00:13:35,100
Tapi itulah yang terjadi
kamu tunjukkan padaku sekarang.

236
00:13:36,533 --> 00:13:39,533
Itulah yang kamu rasakan padaku.

237
00:13:42,633 --> 00:13:46,167
Anda menghindari saya, Anda tidak mau bicara
bagiku kecuali tentang pekerjaan.

238
00:13:46,167 --> 00:13:48,900
Saudara-saudaramu bahkan tidak tahu
kami bertemu kembali di Manila!

239
00:13:49,633 --> 00:13:52,067
Jadi, saya tidak mengerti
kenapa kamu bersikap seperti itu.

240
00:13:56,100 --> 00:13:57,600
Kamu baru saja membuangku.

241
00:14:05,133 --> 00:14:06,633
Kami bahagia, bukan?

242
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:16,000
Apakah itu bukan apa-apa bagimu?

243
00:14:23,133 --> 00:14:24,667
[Menghela napas]

244
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:29,567
Aku sudah melepaskan semua itu
terjadi padaku di masa lalu.

245
00:14:30,567 --> 00:14:32,100
Saya di sini sekarang.

246
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:34,500
Ini Luna yang kukenal.

247
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:41,433
Jika Anda tidak bisa menerimanya,
tidak ada yang bisa kulakukan.

248
00:14:43,567 --> 00:14:46,533
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG LEMBUT DAN DRAMATIK]

249
00:15:08,500 --> 00:15:09,667
Hei, Leon.

250
00:15:12,100 --> 00:15:13,533
Saya pikir kamu akan pulang.

251
00:15:13,533 --> 00:15:16,433
Aku hanya menunggu supirku
untuk mendapatkan mobilnya.

252
00:15:19,467 --> 00:15:22,400
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK TENSE]

253
00:15:32,167 --> 00:15:34,167
- [REVVS MESIN]
- [DUKUM]

254
00:15:34,167 --> 00:15:35,367
[DEKIT BAN]

255
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:44,367
Sandro Soleman?

256
00:15:49,300 --> 00:15:50,367
Apakah kamu kenal dia?

257
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:53,133
Eh... Tidak.

258
00:15:54,133 --> 00:15:55,767
Saya hanya membaca apa yang tertulis.

259
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:58,600
Apakah dia orang lokal?

260
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,600
Tidak, hanya berkunjung.

261
00:16:02,100 --> 00:16:04,300
Putranya saja
melaporkan dia hilang.

262
00:16:05,767 --> 00:16:07,700
Baiklah. Hati-hati di jalan.

263
00:16:09,267 --> 00:16:12,233
[MUSIK TENSE BERLANJUT]

264
00:16:25,667 --> 00:16:27,100
[KLIK KAMERA HP]

265
00:16:27,100 --> 00:16:28,033
[KIKO] Giok!

266
00:16:28,433 --> 00:16:31,100
[KLIK KAMERA HP]

267
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:32,467
- Giok.
- Tunggu!

268
00:16:32,467 --> 00:16:33,633
- Ayo pergi.
- Tunggu, tunggu.

269
00:16:33,633 --> 00:16:34,433
Saya hanya memotret.

270
00:16:34,433 --> 00:16:36,567
Mungkin saya bisa mendapatkannya
beberapa inspirasi

271
00:16:36,567 --> 00:16:38,533
untuk sesi melukis anak-anak.

272
00:16:39,233 --> 00:16:40,000
[KLIK KAMERA HP]

273
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,600
Apakah kamu tidur lebih awal tadi malam?

274
00:16:42,533 --> 00:16:45,667
Ya. Mm, Edward and I
juga tidak begadang lama.

275
00:16:45,667 --> 00:16:47,400
He just wanted me
to tell him stories.

276
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:50,567
We're going home again.

277
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:54,333
Back to the real world.
[Terkekeh]

278
00:16:54,333 --> 00:16:55,533
Ya benar.

279
00:16:56,167 --> 00:16:58,367
Too bad Leon didn't get
to experience this.

280
00:16:58,367 --> 00:17:01,100
If he were here,
itu akan sangat menyenangkan.

281
00:17:02,333 --> 00:17:04,267
- Untuk ya.
- [SNAKE HISSING]

282
00:17:04,267 --> 00:17:05,300
[KIKO GROANS]

283
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:06,867
- Aduh! Giok! Sakit!
- Kiko! Kiko! Kiko!

284
00:17:06,867 --> 00:17:08,300
Apa yang telah terjadi?! Astaga!

285
00:17:08,300 --> 00:17:09,667
- Aku digigit ular!
- You got bitten?! Astaga!

286
00:17:09,667 --> 00:17:11,233
- Oh my god!
- [GROANS]

287
00:17:11,233 --> 00:17:12,367
You got bitten! Kiko!

288
00:17:12,367 --> 00:17:13,633
- Aduh!
- Oh tidak! Apa yang harus saya lakukan?

289
00:17:13,633 --> 00:17:14,700
- Jade...
- What should I do?!

290
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:16,300
- Jade, it hurts!
- Kiko-- Help!

291
00:17:16,333 --> 00:17:17,600
Membantu! Tunggu!

292
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:18,900
Tunggu, tunggu. Bernapas saja.
Tunggu.

293
00:17:18,900 --> 00:17:20,467
Calm down, wait! Tunggu!

294
00:17:20,467 --> 00:17:22,233
- Tunggu, aku melihatnya di film...
- Aduh! Aduh!

295
00:17:22,233 --> 00:17:23,600
...itu ketika kamu digigit
by a snake,

296
00:17:23,600 --> 00:17:24,867
you have to suck
the venom out.

297
00:17:24,867 --> 00:17:26,467
- Kamu akan menyedotnya?!
- Apa?!

298
00:17:26,467 --> 00:17:28,300
I'm not sucking it!
Apa maksudmu menghisapnya?!

299
00:17:28,300 --> 00:17:29,633
- TIDAK! I'm not sucking that!
- Giok!

300
00:17:29,633 --> 00:17:30,567
What if the poison
transfers to me?!

301
00:17:30,567 --> 00:17:31,800
Jade, oh my god!
Saya pikir saya akan mati!

302
00:17:31,800 --> 00:17:33,667
- Tidak, kamu tidak-- Baiklah!
- Aduh! Aduh!

303
00:17:34,367 --> 00:17:35,433
aku akan melakukannya!

304
00:17:35,433 --> 00:17:38,500
aku akan melakukannya! Di Sini! Di Sini!
Oke. [BREATHES HEAVILY]

305
00:17:38,500 --> 00:17:39,600
- Apa?
- Di mana?

306
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:40,400
- [KIKO GROANS]
- Hurry! Ayo!

307
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:41,633
- Duduk! Duduk! Di Sini!
- Aduh! Aduh!

308
00:17:41,633 --> 00:17:43,600
Aku akan menyedotnya! Buru-buru!
Ayo!

309
00:17:43,600 --> 00:17:44,767
- Lift it! Buru-buru.
- Here-- Ouch!

310
00:17:45,467 --> 00:17:46,733
- Apa yang telah terjadi?
- Seni!

311
00:17:46,733 --> 00:17:48,433
Dia digigit ular!

312
00:17:48,467 --> 00:17:49,500
- Snake?!
- [KIKO GRUNTS]

313
00:17:49,500 --> 00:17:50,867
Tunggu, apa warna ular itu?

314
00:17:50,867 --> 00:17:52,867
Apa? It was like...

315
00:17:52,867 --> 00:17:55,800
Jenisnya berwarna hitam dengan bintik-bintik coklat.
Sesuatu seperti itu.

316
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:56,933
- Maybe a wolf snake.
- Hah?!

317
00:17:56,933 --> 00:17:59,733
- [ART] Tapi itu tidak berbisa.
- [KIKO] Ouch! Aduh!

318
00:18:00,333 --> 00:18:02,200
[GROANING CONTINUES]

319
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,500
- [JADE] Kiko?
- Mm?

320
00:18:03,500 --> 00:18:04,933
Apakah kamu mempunyai tanda di pantatmu?

321
00:18:04,933 --> 00:18:06,333
- Hah?
- Hah?

322
00:18:06,333 --> 00:18:08,767
Because my grandpa said
jika kamu mempunyai tanda di pantatmu,

323
00:18:08,767 --> 00:18:09,833
it means bad luck.

324
00:18:09,833 --> 00:18:12,200
Saya tidak memiliki tanda di pantat saya.
Maybe you do!

325
00:18:12,200 --> 00:18:14,700
Saya hanya mengalami kecelakaan
whenever I'm with you.

326
00:18:14,700 --> 00:18:15,900
The time I choked,

327
00:18:15,900 --> 00:18:18,267
when you almost got hit
dengan sepeda motor, lalu ini--

328
00:18:18,267 --> 00:18:19,800
[GROANS] Ouch! Aduh!

329
00:18:19,800 --> 00:18:21,267
That's three times?!
Oh, Ms. Jade,

330
00:18:21,300 --> 00:18:22,567
that's a different kind
nasib buruk.

331
00:18:22,567 --> 00:18:24,567
Hah? What bad luck?

332
00:18:24,567 --> 00:18:26,767
Sari, what is that now?

333
00:18:26,767 --> 00:18:29,267
Sir, that's a belief
of the elders

334
00:18:29,267 --> 00:18:30,767
here in the province.

335
00:18:30,767 --> 00:18:32,967
Ketika dua orang selalu
unlucky together,

336
00:18:32,967 --> 00:18:34,567
it means they're cursed.

337
00:18:34,567 --> 00:18:37,700
Ya, ada keyakinan tertentu
in the provinces.

338
00:18:37,700 --> 00:18:38,933
Oh dear, Ms. Jade.

339
00:18:38,933 --> 00:18:41,367
Jika aku jadi kamu,
I'd have that removed.

340
00:18:41,367 --> 00:18:43,400
I know how to remove it.

341
00:18:43,867 --> 00:18:44,967
Apakah kamu mau?

342
00:18:44,967 --> 00:18:52,200
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK LEMBUT]

343
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:54,867
[GELOMBANG MENGHANCURKAN]

344
00:18:59,233 --> 00:19:05,967
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK LEMBUT]

345
00:19:20,867 --> 00:19:27,833
[MUSIK LEMBUT BERLANJUT]

346
00:19:34,467 --> 00:19:36,867
[GELOMBANG MENGHANCURKAN]

347
00:19:38,833 --> 00:19:42,867
[GELOMBANG MENGHANCURKAN]

348
00:19:45,567 --> 00:19:49,633
[MUSIK LEMBUT BERLANJUT]

349
00:19:49,633 --> 00:19:50,733
[GIO] The bridge...

350
00:19:55,500 --> 00:19:58,000
Anda mengatakan sebelumnya bahwa kami memang begitu
di ujung jembatan yang berlawanan.

351
00:20:03,600 --> 00:20:05,767
I couldn't cross
the bridge, Gio.

352
00:20:08,867 --> 00:20:10,000
Jadi mari kita berhenti.

353
00:20:10,533 --> 00:20:17,500
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK GLUM]

354
00:20:20,367 --> 00:20:24,833
[BOAT ROARING]

355
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:37,967
[Musik GLUM BERLANJUT]

356
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:42,767
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK PENSIF]

357
00:20:45,233 --> 00:20:47,000
[LEON]
<i> Ada yang mencarinya.</i>

358
00:20:49,267 --> 00:20:50,500
<i> Mungkinkah itu keluarganya?</i>

359
00:21:00,633 --> 00:21:03,100
<i> Why are you looking
for my father?</i>

360
00:21:08,733 --> 00:21:11,700
[MUSIK PENSIF BERLANJUT]

361
00:21:18,600 --> 00:21:20,800
[JUSTIN]<i> Kenapa kamu mencarinya
</i> pada kakakku seperti itu?

362
00:21:26,733 --> 00:21:28,567
Maaf maaf! aku tidak melihatmu.
<i> Apakah kamu baik-baik saja?</i>

363
00:21:28,567 --> 00:21:30,133
<i> - Yeah.
- Aku tidak bermaksud demikian.</i>

364
00:21:38,567 --> 00:21:41,567
[MUSIC TURNS TENSE]

365
00:21:49,100 --> 00:21:50,167
Apa itu?

366
00:22:01,167 --> 00:22:03,667
Selamat pagi, Pak.
Apa yang bisa saya bantu?

367
00:22:03,667 --> 00:22:06,233
Saya hanya ingin bertanya
at your front desk.

368
00:22:07,733 --> 00:22:09,167
We don't have anyone in
sekarang.

369
00:22:10,233 --> 00:22:11,600
You can ask me instead.

370
00:22:12,567 --> 00:22:14,200
I work here, too.

371
00:22:16,367 --> 00:22:19,333
Saya ingin tahu apakah saya bisa mempostingnya
beberapa poster hilang di sini.

372
00:22:19,333 --> 00:22:21,267
Oh, maafkan saya, Pak.

373
00:22:21,267 --> 00:22:24,767
Kami hanya memposting aktivitas hotel
on the bulletin board.

374
00:22:24,767 --> 00:22:26,833
But I can tell our staff
tentang hal itu.

375
00:22:26,833 --> 00:22:29,733
Jika kita pernah melihat, eh...

376
00:22:32,367 --> 00:22:33,767
Mr. Sandro?

377
00:22:33,767 --> 00:22:35,200
Sandro Soliman.

378
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:36,867
Ayahku.

379
00:22:37,467 --> 00:22:38,600
Oh baiklah.

380
00:22:39,267 --> 00:22:40,867
I'll tell our staff
to keep an eye out.

381
00:22:41,633 --> 00:22:42,700
Terima kasih.

382
00:22:44,367 --> 00:22:47,333
[MUSIK TENSE BERLANJUT]

383
00:22:57,867 --> 00:23:00,233
Map? Uncle Mike has a folder?

384
00:23:00,233 --> 00:23:02,433
<i>- I'll stay here.
- Apa yang akan kamu lakukan?</i>

385
00:23:02,433 --> 00:23:03,433
<i> Awasi saja.</i>

386
00:23:03,433 --> 00:23:04,800
<i> Kenapa kamu menutupnya
the first time?</i>

387
00:23:04,800 --> 00:23:05,900
<i> Terjadi kebakaran.</i>

388
00:23:05,900 --> 00:23:08,167
<i> Tidak ada jejak apapun
kebakaran di mana saja.</i>

389
00:23:08,167 --> 00:23:10,900
<i> Apapun keputusanmu,
I support it.</i>

390
00:23:10,900 --> 00:23:12,167
<i> Jika kamu masih mencintainya,</i>

391
00:23:12,167 --> 00:23:14,633
<i>find out the answers
untuk semua pertanyaanmu.</i>

392
00:23:14,633 --> 00:23:16,333
<i> Dan gunakan itu untuk memperjuangkannya.</i>

393
00:23:16,333 --> 00:23:18,500
<i>Apa pun yang terjadi,
I'm all for it.</i>

394
00:23:18,500 --> 00:23:20,800
<i>But, she's good
untuk bisnis.</i>

395
00:23:20,800 --> 00:23:22,567
<i>Most importantly,
dia baik untuk hatimu.</i>

396
00:23:22,600 --> 00:23:23,800
<i> Are you...</i>

397
00:23:24,433 --> 00:23:26,733
<i>Are you the ones
siapa yang ingin mematahkan kutukan?</i>

398
00:23:26,733 --> 00:23:28,333
<i> - Tunggu, tidak!
- Tidak!</i>

